snippet.title: Brok the InvestiGator - Access-Ability Summer Showcase Trailer
snippet.description: A mixture of point and click adventure alongside side scrolling beat-em-up, you play as a middle aged alligator detective, in a game that features numerous accessibility options to support blind players.
